<p>5. PROCESS OF DEALS (ORDERS)</p>
<p>Deals in the System are concluded on the basis of Orders placed by Users and in accordance with the conditions determined by the Parties on the basis of the preliminary conditions for the onerous alienation of rights to the Cryptocurrency. At the same time, Crypto Soul, under no circumstances, is a party of the deal. All deals are concluded between Users with information mediation of Crypto Soul.</p>
